{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-jsx","path":"/react/chart/docs/guides/zoom-and-pan/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"react-chart---zoom-and-pan\"><a href=\"#react-chart---zoom-and-pan\" aria-label=\"react chart   zoom and pan permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React Chart - Zoom and Pan</h1>\n<p>Users can zoom and pan (scroll) the React Chart. These actions change the chart's viewport. Mouse and touch gestures are supported.</p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-setup\"><a href=\"#basic-setup\" aria-label=\"basic setup permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic Setup</h2>\n<p>Import the <a href=\"../reference/zoom-and-pan.md\">ZoomAndPan</a> plugin and add it to the <code class=\"language-text\">Chart</code> component to enable zooming and panning.</p>\n<p>Note that the <a href=\"./plugin-overview.md#plugin-order\">plugin order</a> is important.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uncontrolled-mode\"><a href=\"#uncontrolled-mode\" aria-label=\"uncontrolled mode permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Uncontrolled Mode</h3>\n<p>In uncontrolled mode, add the <code class=\"language-text\">ZoomAndPan</code> plugin to the <code class=\"language-text\">Chart</code> component.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"zoom-pan/uncontrolled\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h3 id=\"controlled-mode\"><a href=\"#controlled-mode\" aria-label=\"controlled mode permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Controlled Mode</h3>\n<p>In the controlled mode, pass the viewport's boundaries to the <code class=\"language-text\">ZoomAndPan</code> plugin's <code class=\"language-text\">viewport</code> property and handle the <code class=\"language-text\">onViewportChange</code> event to control zoom and pan.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"zoom-pan/controlled\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h2 id=\"enable-zooming-or-panning-inidividually\"><a href=\"#enable-zooming-or-panning-inidividually\" aria-label=\"enable zooming or panning inidividually permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable Zooming or Panning Inidividually</h2>\n<p>Use the <code class=\"language-text\">interactionWithArguments</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">interactionWithValues</code> properties to enable zooming and/or panning for individual scales.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"zoom-pan/datetime\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h2 id=\"zoom-by-selecting-a-region\"><a href=\"#zoom-by-selecting-a-region\" aria-label=\"zoom by selecting a region permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Zoom by Selecting a Region</h2>\n<p>Users can drag the mouse across an area while pressing the <code class=\"language-text\">zoomRegionKey</code> to zoom this area. Zooming is applied when the mouse button is released.</p>","fields":{"technology":"react/chart","section":"docs"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"react/chart/docs/guides/zoom-and-pan/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","3662068265"]}